'''Lla Cṛifa''', deg yisem ines n tidett '''Wardya Bucemlal''', tluled deg tama n yelmayen (di Burǧ Bu Ɛarriǧ) aseggwas n 1926. Nettat tacenayt taqbaylit yellan seg tmezwura yesulin ccan n ccna n teqbyalit.

== Tameddurt-is[beddel]==

Akken id ttεawad nettat s yimad-is, asmi tella tamctuḥt, tekes tiγeṭṭen deg tmizar n xwali-s. Dγa iwakken ad sɛeddi lweqt, ur tḥbez ara deg ucewwaq. Xali-s is isellen yesarwaya-s tiyita. Imiren, di tmurt n leqbayel, d lɛib i teqcict ad tecnnu.

Deg taddart, anda tesla i yenzizen ubendayer, aksum-is ad yecceruw, dγa ad-taɛnu afrag anda yella wurar iwakken ad-teccnu ukud lxalat nniden.
Asmi tesawwed 18 isegwasen di laɛmer-is, teǧǧa tamurt-is, teṭṭef abrid-is ar Lzzayer tamanaγt. Dγa, deg tmaccint i-tt yewwin ar Lezzayer, tewwid acewwiq anda is teqqar " Bqa ɛla xir ay Aqbu, tura iffut zhu".

Kra n lweqt kkan mid sawwed ar Lezzayer, tameṭṭut n xali-s Lla Yamina n Yiγil Aεli, tewwi-tt ar Radyu anda tebda dγa abrid is di ccna. Tuffa di Radyu Lla Zina Tawertilanit, Lla Wenissa Taxerffeliwt. Cwit kkan terna-d Lla Lǧida Tamuqrant, Ǧamila, Ḥnifa.
Tettεwaded belli di lweqt-nni yellan kkan "srid" (en direct) ulac asekles.

